{"tid":527813,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［求救］［拼圖］係唔岩定正常？","createTime":"2018-01-13T05:33:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-13T05:44:30.000Z","uid":119174,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f248cddf09acf1cfa6c79e3ce9398c3f946cc543","tid":527813,"uid":119174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T05:33:26.000Z","msg":"有無人砌過呢個？<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/13/132722_6482a82b335d145b3ad9b4801abcaf31.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F13%2F132722_6482a82b335d145b3ad9b4801abcaf31.png&h=05238815&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個砌圖岩岩先開始砌就發現唔對路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/13/132830_6f79fe4080edfaa7a46742ad2afece75.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F13%2F132830_6f79fe4080edfaa7a46742ad2afece75.png&h=00da2dc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n明明呢個正正常常<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/13/132915_1ea3da9b25a23d4a2a4c7519382a8da2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F13%2F132915_1ea3da9b25a23d4a2a4c7519382a8da2.png&h=1cd9c886&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n然後發現呢啲波浪線砌圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為係邊位既砌圖仲想呃自己無事 可能係特色呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/13/133026_ae9ee6e9531e5230f6f4fff58b1eb4a0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F13%2F133026_ae9ee6e9531e5230f6f4fff58b1eb4a0.png&h=f13ad9f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中間既砌圖圖會又咁掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無人可以話我知點解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係正常定玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc5f86c83c1280b19e7490c3b4a52bc3152ab16f","tid":527813,"uid":119174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T05:35:23.000Z","msg":"求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a65c09403468d1ed3775c7529c6cf0b52322b44","tid":527813,"uid":119174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T05:38:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf4157912bc63f820637c2b20f818537f64490c5","tid":527813,"uid":119174,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T05:38:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc22f2296e44d2e3cd6757960d429dd4b33b864d","tid":527813,"uid":29689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T05:40:10.000Z","msg":"想問呢到係咪得我一個黑人問號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bddcbe1eb410eaf83d81578983f4200c8ae050c4","tid":527813,"uid":129453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T05:40:34.000Z","msg":"其實應該冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢都係同一張圖cut出黎<br />\n如果係邊位歪既你唔順眼咪cut直佢"},{"pid":"51f8af8758e44c0b81bf772726f8d9c46fe42b3d","tid":527813,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T05:40:39.000Z","msg":"邊到買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37f943557800f0e734304a5fbfc9a6f4b9427899","tid":527813,"uid":985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T05:41:46.000Z","msg":"呢d野 最好唔好買劣質大陸貨"},{"pid":"14c24ee6933cc26eba8c82d68b3df32be6b7de57","tid":527813,"uid":119174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bddcbe1eb410eaf83d81578983f4200c8ae050c4","tid":527813,"uid":1